channel.title: Unkn0wnscape [317] New Release
channel.description:
[center][size=24pt]UNKN0WNSCAPE[/size][/center]
Hey guys this is my first source. Please dont flame if you dont like it. I know its not the best but it's pretty good for my first time. If this is in the wrong section please move it because this is the download for the client so you can connect to me. I didnt know where to put it. Anyways here it is.
[b][u][size=18pt]FEATURES[/size][/u][/b] - Working Clan chat (by commands) - Pest Control, Fight pits, Barrows and Assualt all work! - Heaps of bosses - Awesome home - Working D claws + 4x Spec - Working Godswords with stance and Right specials - All pvp armour - Dragon Hai robes - Anchor - Working Altars
[size=18pt][b][u]SKILLS[/u][/b][/size] - 100% Agility - 100% Melee - 100% Magic - 100% Range - 100% Theiving - 100% Prayer - 100% Woodcutting - 100% Firemaking - 100% Mining - 100% Runecrafting - 80% Slayer - 60% Fletching - 60% Crafting - 60% Smithing - 60% Cooking - 20% Fishing - 0% Farming and Herblore ( The reason being I havent played runescape for a long time and when I did play it I never did farming or herblore so I have no idea how it works which means I cant exactly code it. So yeah, I'll probably work out farming and herblore soon and I'll code it in.)
[center][size=18pt]Picture time![/size][/center]
Home! Thanks to PvP 317 X for the idea! :) [IMG]http://i54.tinypic.com/2hz1gzq.png[/img]
Full Vestas! [IMG]http://i56.tinypic.com/264i0qa.png[/img]
Full Zuriels! [IMG]http://i56.tinypic.com/wgx5br.png[/img]
Full Statius! [IMG]http://i51.tinypic.com/68u0xs.png[/img]
Full Morrigans! [IMG]http://i53.tinypic.com/15y9dhd.png[/img]
New HD whip model! [IMG]http://i54.tinypic.com/li8uu.png[/img]
Awesome Pest Control Interface (Fight Pits has the same interface) [IMG]http://i52.tinypic.com/2n22vb9.png[/img]
Working Agility (One of many skills 100% working) [IMG]http://i51.tinypic.com/2qs6o74.png[/img]
Working Friends List + Working Private chat with split chat. [IMG]http://i52.tinypic.com/2qx3n6c.png[/img]
D claws spec 4x Hit! [IMG]http://i54.tinypic.com/bi2lp5.png[/img]
Working GodSword specs [IMG]http://i51.tinypic.com/zsr09g.png[/img]
All Emotes working! ( This is zombie walk ) [IMG]http://i51.tinypic.com/34s02dw.png[/img]
Dragon Hai robes, Anchor and Awesome quest tab! [IMG]http://i52.tinypic.com/978xm0.png[/img]
Credits 50% to me. ( I added in theving, fully working combat, most teleports in the spellbook and all the boses) 2% PvP 317 X ( for the home idea. ) 8% Lancer (One of my admins for helping me get players and giving me a few economy tips and such) 20% Delta (Obviously for the base) 20% Everyone on mopar ( For all the tutorials )
Download Link - Coming soon! ( I just fixing up a few things before I release it but if you like it keep looking out for the download! )
